  Sections:
  - TextHeading: Welcome
    TextSubheading: 
    TextBody: Single-player–focused prototype combining Bomberman-style arena play and FPS combat (Unity FPS Microgame + MasterBlaster). Primary scene — Assets/Scenes/MasterBlaster/MasterBlaster_FPS.unity
    LinkName: 
    LinkUrl: 
    PingObjectName: 
    PingObjectGuid: 
    MenuItemName: 
    MenuItemPath: 
  - TextHeading: Coursework deliverables
    TextSubheading: 
    TextBody: Replace these links after you upload your build and a source zip of the project.
    LinkName: Windows build (placeholder)
    LinkUrl: https://REPLACE-WITH-YOUR-WINDOWS-BUILD-LINK.example.com
    PingObjectName: 
